name: The Unsung
description:
MPEG-4 movie
2500 × 3540 px

Digital collage finished on November 11, 2021.


This collage was made a day after Indonesia National Heroes' Day. I read an article that morning about there are only 15 women heroes from 195 national heroes, It makes me wonder, whether women's contribution is less than 10% for this country? of course I don't think so.


Main Images from rijksmuseum.nl, and the rest from other sites on the internet.

Studio Portrait of a Javanese Woman. Creator: Kassian Céphas. Date: 1867 - 1910.
